<section xml:id="soc" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0">
    <title>Summary of changes</title>
    <para>This section lists the changes of The &product; Administrator Guide.</para>
    <section xml:id="pe-changes" condition="pe">
        <title>Version 6 LTS - 7.0</title>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Changes in product:</title>
            <para/>
        </formalpara>
        <para>Several features that are available in &product; 6 LTS are not yet available in &abbrev; &version;. For a list of features that are available in &abbrev; 6 LTS but not in &version; see <olink targetdoc="syslog-ng-pe-guide-whatsnew" targetptr="features-not-available"/>.</para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="supported-platforms"/> has been updated.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="chapter-enrich-data"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="configuring-destinations-stomp"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="chapter-correlating-log-messages"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="configuring-destinations-http"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="configuring-destinations-http-nonjava"/> has been added to the document.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="what-is-new-patterndb-v5"/>, <xref linkend="element-patterndb-create-context"/>,  has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-patterndb"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="sql-option-dbd-option"/> has been added to <xref linkend="configuring-destinations-sql"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="inline-objects"/> has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-configuration-file"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="embedded-objects"/> has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-configuration-file"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="anonymizing-credit-card-numbers"/> has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-manipulating-messages"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="parser-syslog"/> has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-parsers"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="date-parser"/> has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-parsers"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para><xref linkend="apache-access-log-parser"/> has been added to <xref linkend="chapter-parsers"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>New options of the <parameter>set()</parameter> rewrite operator have been added to <xref linkend="rewrite-set"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>A rewrite operator to unset fields has been added to <xref linkend="rewrite-unset"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>A template function that formats name-value pairs as ArcSight Common Event Format extension has been added to <xref linkend="template-function-format-cef-extension"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Numerical template functions that work on numerical values of a correlation context have been added to <xref linkend="template-function-numerical"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>inherit-environment()</parameter> option has been added to <xref linkend="configuring-source-program"/> and <xref linkend="configuring-destinations-program"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>The <parameter>multi-line-mode()</parameter> option has been added to <xref linkend="reference-source-file"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>New parsers have been added to <xref linkend="syslog-ng-patterndb-using-parsers"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>You can use human-readable units when setting configuration options, for example, <userinput>log-fifo-size(2Mb)</userinput>. For details, see <xref linkend="configuration-syntax-notes"/>.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
        <formalpara>
            <title>Changes in documentation:</title>
            <para/>
        </formalpara>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>Several corrections and editorial changes.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </section>
</section>
